<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="10" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,718,961]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,287,718,745]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">Comments.</emphasis>
Broun based this species on two specimens, one of which was in the BMNH that we designated as the 
<typeStatus box="[151,254,755,781]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">lectotype</typeStatus>
to stabilise the epithet. Another specimen in the Broun collection from Titirangi, was not considered a 
<typeStatus box="[151,238,791,817]" pageId="9" pageNumber="10">syntype</typeStatus>
because it was collected at a much later date.
</paragraph>
